=retro", "created": 1667815923, "last_modified": 1667815923}, "last_reply_by": "isc", "last_touched": 1703931220, "title": "要坐十几个小时的火车，大伙有什么推荐的电影或者单机游戏吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1004544", "created": 1703863808, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1703863808, "replies": 43, "id": 1004544}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 213691, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4063, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 157703, "username": "yanaraika", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yanaraika", "website": "morgancortney@protonmail.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9471/6d30/157703_mini.png?m=1456742889", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9471/6d30/157703_normal.png?m=1456742889", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9471/6d30/157703_large.png?m=1456742889", "created": 1454308685, "last_modified": 1456742889}, "last_reply_by": "colorwin", "last_touched": 1703926266, "title": "怎么才能给在小县城的老人找到年轻力壮的护工保姆？有没有跨地保姆平台？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1004563", "created": 1703896001, "deleted": 0, "content": "和很多 V2EX 的朋友一样，楼主在大城市写码但是父母在小县城养老。上次回县城发现小县城老龄化非常严重，想找一个靠谱的每天 8-10 小时做个午饭晚饭、打扫家务、陪半失能老人下医院的保姆，结果来应聘的都是 50 多岁的，而且试了两天父母说天天推销无证膏药想骗老人钱。问了一圈本地老人都是一样的问题。根本问题就是本地基本没几个青壮年，都去大城市打工了。突发奇想有没有跨地保姆平台，每个月出 1 万甚至更高+解决小县城租房把其他地区的专业保姆雇佣到小县城，按理说应该是一个不错的生意，想问问 V 友们有没有想法", "content_rendered": "和很多 V2EX 的朋友一样，楼主在大城市写码但是父母在小县城养老。上次回县城发现小县城老龄化非常严重，想找一个靠谱的每天 8-10 小时做个午饭晚饭、打扫家务、陪半失能老人下医院的保姆，结果来应聘的都是 50 多岁的，而且试了两天父母说天天推销无证膏药想骗老人钱。问了一圈本地老人都是一样的问题。根本问题就是本地基本没几个青壮年，都去大城市打工了。突发奇想有没有跨地保姆平台，每个月出 1 万甚至更高+解决小县城租房把其他地区的专业保姆雇佣到小县城，按理说应该是一个不错的生意，想问问 V 友们有没有想法", "last_modified": 1703896001, "replies": 30, "id": 1004563}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 60606, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8786, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 647438, "username": "ieesk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ieesk", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/55d5e3b0a4b1d0dff654f80392ae127f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/55d5e3b0a4b1d0dff654f80392ae127f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/55d5e3b0a4b1d0dff654f80392ae127f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1694052509, "last_modified": 1694052509}, "last_reply_by": "dioxide", "last_touched": 1703894196, "title": "这才是防御性编程", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1004506", "created": 1703848445, "deleted": 0, "content": "![x1.jpg]( https://p.sda1.dev/14/af628e5dc226c86187f52f369d942c7f/x1.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"x1.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://p.sda1.dev/14/af628e5dc226c86187f52f369d942c7f/x1.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1703848668, "replies": 30, "id": 1004506}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 15615, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146", "stars": 2913, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 54671, "username": "9yu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/9yu", "website": "https://mayo.rocks", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "mayocream", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/793e/947e/54671_mini.png?m=1634406754", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/793e/947e/54671_normal.png?m=1634406754", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/793e/947e/54671_large.png?m=1634406754", "created": 1390307080, "last_modified": 1634406754}, "last_reply_by": "aneureka", "last_touched": 1703932920, "title": "在国内拿到日本 Mercari Offer", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1004606", "created": 1703914631, "deleted": 0, "content": "无职了将近一年，11 月我终于鼓起勇气开始找 Base 在东京的 Remote 的工作，工作机会少得可怜，一个是位于日本的研发中心本来就很少，一个是年底了可能很多公司都 Hiring Freeze 了，我只投了 3 家公司，拿到了 Mercari 的面试机会。\r\n\r\nMercari 的面试流程很慢，Hackerrank 接着一轮 90 分钟两位面试官的 Technical Interview ，之后是 Manager 以及和 Head of Engineering 的 Culture Fit 。面试有 Options 可选英语或日语面试，我选择既可以英语也可以日语面试，不过是用英语准备的 Behavior Questions ，Manager 面的面试官是日本人所以最后用日语简单问了问题。\r\n\r\n面试感觉不错，反馈 All positive 但是 Recruiter 告诉我内部有一个 Headcount issue 以及 Shuffling of priorities ，感觉希望渺茫不过 Recruiter 还是很积极地和我 Follow up ，本来已经不抱什么希望了，一周后和我 Catchup 告诉我他们解决了 Headcount issue 并且想要招我，我找了前同事来做 Reference 之后等审批 Offer ，Recruiter 和我说很难 Match 我之前的薪资不过一周后我拿到了非常满意的 Written Offer ，当天我就签字接下了。\r\n\r\n对比上家强制要求 Onsite ，Mercari 可以自由选择 Remote 或 Onsite ，我投的岗位所在的 Team 大家都是 Remote 所以我也要在东京 Remote 工作！\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nMercari sponsor 高度专门 visa ，已经提交完材料等办在留了。", "content_rendered": "<p>无职了将近一年，11 月我终于鼓起勇气开始找 Base 在东京的 Remote 的工作，工作机会少得可怜，一个是位于日本的研发中心本来就很少，一个是年底了可能很多公司都 Hiring Freeze 了，我只投了 3 家公司，拿到了 Mercari 的面试机会。</p>\n<p>Mercari 的面试流程很慢，Hackerrank 接着一轮 90 分钟两位面试官的 Technical Interview ，之后是 Manager 以及和 Head of Engineering 的 Culture Fit 。面试有 Options 可选英语或日语面试，我选择既可以英语也可以日语面试，不过是用英语准备的 Behavior Questions ，Manager 面的面试官是日本人所以最后用日语简单问了问题。</p>\n<p>面试感觉不错，反馈 All positive 但是 Recruiter 告诉我内部有一个 Headcount issue 以及 Shuffling of priorities ，感觉希望渺茫不过 Recruiter 还是很积极地和我 Follow up ，本来已经不抱什么希望了，一周后和我 Catchup 告诉我他们解决了 Headcount issue 并且想要招我，我找了前同事来做 Reference 之后等审批 Offer ，Recruiter 和我说很难 Match 我之前的薪资不过一周后我拿到了非常满意的 Written Offer ，当天我就签字接下了。</p>\n<p>对比上家强制要求 Onsite ，Mercari 可以自由选择 Remote 或 Onsite ，我投的岗位所在的 Team 大家都是 Remote 所以我也要在东京 Remote 工作！</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>Mercari sponsor 高度专门 visa ，已经提交完材料等办在留了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1703914631, "replies": 26, "id": 1004606}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 60606, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8786, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 35624, "username": "xuelang", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuelang", "website": "https://selfboot.cn", "twitter": "selfboots", "psn": "", "github": "selfboot", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "C++ 后台开发～\r\nAI 粉丝，人机结合实践者～\r\n\r\n法律科普小能手\r\n家有律师\r\nV2EX 法律咨询解答小能手", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b568/e3db/35624_mini.png?m=1686366600", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b568/e3db/35624_normal.png?m=1686366600", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b568/e3db/35624_large.png?m=1686366600", "created": 1362928874, "last_modified": 1686366600}, "last_reply_by": "myqoo", "last_touched"